        "nodes": [
            {
                "parameters": {
                    "promptType": "define",
                    "text": "=## CRO ANALYSIS REQUEST\n\n**Client:** {{ $json.client_name }}\n**Website:** {{ $json.website }}\n**Report Period:** {{ $json.reportMonth }}\n**Primary Conversion Event:** {{ $json.primary_conversion_event }}\n\n---\n\n## DATA FOR ANALYSIS\n\n### Google Analytics 4 Data:\n```json\n{{ JSON.stringify($json.ga4, null, 2) }}\n```\n\n### Microsoft Clarity Behavior Data:\n```json\n{{ JSON.stringify($json.clarity, null, 2) }}\n```\n\n---\n\n## REQUIRED OUTPUT FORMAT\n\nProvide your analysis in the following markdown structure:\n\n# {{ $json.client_name }} — CRO Insights ({{ $json.reportMonth }})\n\n## 1. Performance Overview\n- Total Sessions: [number]\n- Total Users: [number]\n- Conversions ({{ $json.primary_conversion_event }}): [number]\n- Sitewide Conversion Rate: [percentage]\n- Mobile vs Desktop conversion comparison\n- Top 3 converting landing pages\n- Bottom 3 converting landing pages\n\n## 2. Behavioral Findings (Clarity)\n- Pages with highest rage click density (and why it matters)\n- Pages with low scroll depth (< 50%)\n- Device-specific UX issues identified\n- Average engagement time analysis\n\n## 3. Hypotheses (What Might Be Going Wrong)\nFor each hypothesis:\n- H1: [Hypothesis statement]\n  - Evidence: [Data supporting this]\n  - Confidence: [High/Medium/Low]\n\n## 4. Recommended Actions\nFor each recommendation (3-5 total):\n| Page/Section | Issue Identified | Suggested Change | Expected Impact | Priority |\n|-------------|-----------------|------------------|-----------------|----------|\n| [specific page] | [specific issue] | [specific fix] | [qualitative] | [High/Med/Low] |\n\n## 5. Priority Actions for Next Month\n1. [Most impactful action]\n2. [Second priority]\n3. [Third priority]\n\n## 6. Dashboard Links for Manual Review\n- [Clarity Dashboard Link placeholder]\n- [GA4 Dashboard Link placeholder]\n\n---\nGenerate the complete report now.",
                    "options": {
                        "systemMessage": "You are a Senior Conversion Rate Optimization (CRO) Specialist with 10+ years of experience analyzing website behavior data and improving conversion funnels.\n\n## YOUR EXPERTISE:\n- Interpreting Google Analytics 4 metrics (sessions, users, conversions, device breakdowns)\n- Analyzing Microsoft Clarity behavioral data (rage clicks, dead clicks, scroll depth, engagement time)\n- Identifying UX friction points and conversion blockers\n- Formulating data-driven hypotheses\n- Prioritizing recommendations by impact vs effort\n\n## YOUR ANALYSIS APPROACH:\n1. Start with the conversion funnel overview\n2. Identify statistical anomalies and outliers\n3. Correlate behavior data with conversion drops\n4. Focus on actionable, specific recommendations\n5. Prioritize quick wins vs long-term improvements\n\n## OUTPUT REQUIREMENTS:\n- Use clear, non-technical language suitable for marketers\n- Be specific about pages, metrics, and percentages\n- Provide concrete recommendations, not vague suggestions\n- Include expected impact estimates (qualitative)\n- Format as markdown with clear sections",
